import React from 'react';

export default function MenuIcon() {
  return (
    <svg
      width='50px'
      height='50px'
      viewBox='0 0 150 125'
      version='1.1'
      xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
    >
      <g
        id='Page-1'
        stroke='none'
        stroke-width='1'
        fill='none'
        fill-rule='evenodd'
      >
        <g id='Group' fill='#1d2b37'>
          <rect id='Rectangle-8' x='0' y='0' width='150' height='25'></rect>
          <rect
            id='Rectangle-8-Copy'
            x='0'
            y='50'
            width='150'
            height='25'
          ></rect>
          <rect
            id='Rectangle-8-Copy-2'
            x='0'
            y='100'
            width='150'
            height='25'
          ></rect>
        </g>
      </g>
    </svg>
  );
}
